# 🚀 Day 13 – Debugging Performance Issues & Inefficient Code in Python
### Python Debugging Lab (14-Day Series)

Today I focused on debugging performance issues in Python code. Sometimes code runs correctly but becomes very slow when working with large datasets. Learning to identify inefficient patterns and optimize them is an important skill for data professionals and engineers.

